Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,This time, we have invited 12 students\Nfrom Nogizaka 3rd grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:08.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,A total of 15 students will have fun\Nlearning English for 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,In the self-introduction that will be\Nheld from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:18.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,you will be told the three English\Nsentences that you have just learned in\Nyour room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,In addition, you will be asked to ask a\Nquestion to get to know the other\Nperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:26.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here is the question that can be used\Nthere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kubo-san, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,What do you do on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,What do you do on your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:40.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please answer what you do on your day\Noff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,For example, if you're going to watch a\Nmovie, Ozono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's good, that's good. You don't\Nhave to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sensei, please listen to me until the\Nend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:58.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:01.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:04.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Movies are called watch movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:07.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Actually, movies were a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please answer without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, the lyrics of a famous\NJapanese song will be announced in\NEnglish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:25.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,The members will translate the English\Nlyrics and guess what song it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:33.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ozono, Ms. Nojo, and Ms. Ito got the\Ncorrect answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,The last one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nakamura-san, there's only one person\Nleft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,A happy song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,There's no such song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:51.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Oh, how happy we would be."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Sekai shiawase no uta."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:55.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's the part you're best at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:03.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,For Ms Nakamura who still doesn't know\Nthe answer, let's ask Ms Ozono to\Ntranslate it into Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, how happy we would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You understood it perfectly, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You still didn't get it. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,What was that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You sang that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:31.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:35.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:37.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,That was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:39.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,I have to say it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's hard to be on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Can you sing for her in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.73,ASS,,0,0,0,,Sing for her in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Under the big tree"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please sing it in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,Then maybe she will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:13.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Under the big tree"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,You really don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,The answer is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Under the big chestnut tree"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:25.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,The word that we want the 3rd generation\Nto remember is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,"How"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,"How to"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,What does "How to" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,You've heard of it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:42.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you just sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you just sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.31,ASS,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good? Sing that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:04:00.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,How many, how much, how much do you\Nwant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,How many, how much, how much do you\Nwant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you learn it at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,How many, how much, how much do you\Nwant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:16.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,But since it's "How to" you often say\N"How to bon" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,She's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,It means how to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:29.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,For example, how to play tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, how to play tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,How to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:41.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, Nick will appear and have a\Nconversation using "how to" and\N"something".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:48.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nick asks, "Can you teach me how to do\N'something'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nick says, "I'll show you how to do\N'something'."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's teach Nick the correct way to do\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,When you teach with gestures, the\Nexpression you use is familiar to the\Nregular 3 people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:12.15,ASS,,0,0,0,,For example, if it's how to eat sushi,\Nsay "like this" and teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,First up is Ms. Ozono and Ms. Mukai.\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,How do you do sumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,How do you do sumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Say this properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,How do you do sumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how to sumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a sumo wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:46.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a sumo wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Is it hand clapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ozono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Why are they silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,You learned it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're pushing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,So now you are satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.13,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:30.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,3 regular members will be the captains,\Nand the game will be split into 3 teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:38.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,The team that wins the game will receive\Na King of Rokkeben, Jojoen Bento as a\Nreward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:43.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,However, the losing team will receive a\Nsevere punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kubo, I heard from Wada-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was studying for a test and I was\Nwatching Nogieigo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,I got a question and I was able to\Nanswer it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,What is this? The teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,The teacher is Kubo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,I got "Like this"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's useful for the test, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,From the various things in the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:22.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nick brings what he said in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Lend-a-thing race"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:29.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,Each team selects one person and plays\Nagainst three people at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,The team that brings the right thing\Nwill get 5 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is the third round.
