Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:23.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,The last is Team Kawago vs. Team Wada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.43,ASS,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,There is still a secret weapon, OZONO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:40.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,OZONO is very scared because it is a\Npass to the ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:44.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yoda is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Kubo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:50.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh! Tsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,You can get it firmly, Kubo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,OZONO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,What's Yoda's number?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:14.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Team Wada gets number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:16.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,The answer is Miss Kubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,I got number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:19.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, H.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:21.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, Kubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:24.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Kubo looks like he's going\Nto collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:25.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:28.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, Kanbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:29.33,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:32.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's only Kanbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:33.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:37.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:40.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even with shoes, H will come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:43.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,But, unfortunately, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:49.71,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for the game to resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:51.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Well then, Oozora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:53.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Cameraman, please step back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:58.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make a place for you to be\Nspoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,You've never done this before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:03.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Hiding behind the cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:04.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,You've never done this before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,You didn't have a cameraman at school,\Ndid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:10.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Kawako's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:17.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,You're throwing it while smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.44,ASS,,0,0,0,,Well then, Yoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:21.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:23.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Kawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:29.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:33.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,You're not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:35.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:39.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's starting to sound like Panko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:51.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,If it's like this, just don't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:53.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Just don't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:56.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Is this how you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:24:03.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a bomb, it's a line that's\Ncoming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:07.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:10.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:14.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't Mukai good too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nakamura was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:24.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,Unlike how it looks, Miss Kubo got the\Ncorrect answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:27.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,Will she get the correct answer this\Ntime?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.63,0:24:29.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is D.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:31.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:32.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,D.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.63,0:24:35.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,The second one is H.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:37.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,So it's D.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.63,0:24:41.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's use the image of the whole body\Nand try to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.63,0:24:42.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:45.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want you to guess this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.63,0:24:47.63,ASS,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:47.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,You don't want to fight with everyone,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:52.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't know which one to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:54.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,There's only one word that came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.20,0:24:56.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's not a word, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:58.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Third"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.20,0:25:00.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a nice try, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.20,0:25:02.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's not in this word.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.20,0:25:04.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.20,0:25:06.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nice try. Very nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:08.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.20,0:25:10.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Team Power-Go's attack is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:12.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Of course, the target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:14.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:16.20,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.46,0:25:18.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watch out when you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.46,0:25:20.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.46,0:25:22.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.46,0:25:24.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.46,0:25:26.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.46,0:25:35.46,ASS,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.46,0:25:37.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Umezawa got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.37,0:25:42.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Team Wada got the 3rd letter. Will it be\Nthe correct answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.37,0:25:44.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,The 4th letter is "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.37,0:25:47.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.37,0:25:51.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.37,0:25:54.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's imagine the whole picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.37,0:25:55.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:57.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.37,0:26:00.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,What is the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.37,0:26:02.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.37,0:26:04.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't say the meaning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.37,0:26:05.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't say the meaning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.89,0:26:10.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,No.1 is C. And No.3 is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.89,0:26:12.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Child. What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.89,0:26:15.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.89,0:26:23.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted someone to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.89,0:26:26.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted someone to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.89,0:26:28.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.89,0:26:32.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, Team Wada wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.89,0:26:35.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Team Wada wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.86,0:26:42.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,After the second round, as you can see,\Nthe team spirit has been taken away a\Nlittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.86,0:26:48.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,And the final match is the obstacle\Nrelay in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.86,0:26:57.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,The team with the best time wins by\Nclearing the course with five obstacles\Nin relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.86,0:27:00.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,However, the button is the A word.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:04.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,Write the word on the back of the next\Nrunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.05,0:27:13.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,If you can get the right answer, the\Nnext runner will give you another\Nquestion, and you'll have to clear the\Nobstacle course and pass it on to the\Nnext runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.05,0:27:20.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,You get 15 points for first place, 10\Npoints for second place, and 5 points\Nfor third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.05,0:27:26.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,At this point, the possibility of\Nwinning the team farm is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.05,0:27:28.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.05,0:27:31.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,Next up is Team Wada.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.05,0:27:33.05,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll challenge you in the order you see\Nhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.35,0:27:37.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,The top batter is Mukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.35,0:27:39.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, Niku-san, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.35,0:27:44.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.35,0:27:48.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone is struggling at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.35,0:27:51.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:54.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted Mukai to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.35,0:28:00.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,When Mukai does something, everyone\Nlaughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.35,0:28:01.35,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's good!
