Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.76,0:28:18.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,W?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.76,0:28:21.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ton
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.76,0:28:22.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.76,0:28:23.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.76,0:28:28.76,ASS,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.76,0:28:29.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,T
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:31.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:33.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,The next keyword is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:39.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone is having a hard time with this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.07,0:28:41.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.07,0:28:43.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? You're stammering
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.07,0:28:44.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you hit your head?
