Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.07,0:28:48.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.07,0:28:51.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Will it come out? Will it come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.07,0:28:52.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,It came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.07,0:28:55.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,Wada-chan
