Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.34,0:29:01.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:04.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.34,0:29:06.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
