Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.34,0:29:15.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.34,0:29:17.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.34,0:29:19.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,This really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.34,0:29:22.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, jump! Jump straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.34,0:29:25.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.34,0:29:29.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it\Nhurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.91,0:29:32.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's hard to write, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.91,0:29:34.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
