Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.91,0:29:37.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.91,0:29:39.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.91,0:29:43.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Next keyword.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.91,0:29:45.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.91,0:29:48.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's not scary this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.91,0:29:50.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.91,0:29:53.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's the best so far.
