Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.37,0:30:48.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,E?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.37,0:30:49.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, A
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.37,0:30:50.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, A?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:51.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,T, F
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.37,0:30:53.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,T, E, A
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.37,0:30:55.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, T
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.37,0:30:57.37,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, E
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.37,0:30:58.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,T, F
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.49,0:31:03.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, A, T
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.49,0:31:05.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, A, T
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.49,0:31:07.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.49,0:31:10.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,E, A, E
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.49,0:31:13.49,ASS,,0,0,0,,Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.49,0:31:16.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, what is the correct answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.28,0:31:18.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,How many seconds was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:20.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,34 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.28,0:31:24.28,ASS,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.30,0:31:28.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, the final result announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.30,0:31:30.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,First is 3rd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:32.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:34.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,25 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.30,0:31:36.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Nojo team!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.30,0:31:38.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,We did our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.30,0:31:40.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,We did our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.30,0:31:42.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought Nojo was 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.30,0:31:44.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,Why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.30,0:31:50.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, who is the winning team?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.30,0:31:54.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,1st place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.74,0:31:58.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,51 points for Team Wada!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.36,0:32:12.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Team Wada won by a landslide with "King\Nof Rokeben" and "Jojoen Mentouga".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.36,0:32:15.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,And the last team is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.36,0:32:18.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.36,0:32:20.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.36,0:32:25.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,How was it? What did you dislike the\Nmost?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:27.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't like dodgeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.36,0:32:28.36,ASS,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.36,0:32:32.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't like the game where you have to\Nhit the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.19,0:32:35.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.19,0:32:39.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,Was it your dream to be a triathlete?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.19,0:32:41.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wasn't good at English.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.19,0:32:44.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,But it was fun to play while exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.19,0:32:46.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I wanted to learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.19,0:32:51.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, hit the ball with both\Nhands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.19,0:32:53.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,Next time, hit the ball with your left\Nhand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.19,0:32:55.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to hit the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.67,0:33:03.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Next time, we will show you the\Nunreleased scenes of the special that\Nthe 3rd generation didn't get to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.67,0:33:07.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,The scenes that were cut off from\Nclasses and games are repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:17.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,The special that the 3rd generation came\Nto Nogiei after 2 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.67,0:33:23.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,This time, we will show you a lot of\Nunreleased scenes that were not included\Nin the special.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.54,0:33:31.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,First of all, let's start with the self-\Nintroduction in the English of the 3rd\Ngeneration, which was broadcast on the\NJuly special.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.54,0:33:39.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Introduce your name, birthplace,\Nnickname to the other person as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.54,0:33:48.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,In addition, the rule that you have to\Nask one question to know the other\Nperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.54,0:33:50.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,In the July special,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:34:01.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,First of all, Miss Maya and Miss Nojo,\Nrock-paper-scissors in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:03.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,These two did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.96,0:34:06.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Rock, scissors, scissors, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:10.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.96,0:34:12.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:14.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ozora-san didn't say it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.96,0:34:15.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.03,0:34:19.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissor, scissor, scissor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.03,0:34:24.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Ozono-san, it's not good to do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:27.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Try to say it with rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.03,0:34:30.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissor, scissor, scissor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.03,0:34:32.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,You can't do rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.03,0:34:38.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,After rock-paper-scissors, Ms. Ozono\Nwill introduce herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.03,0:34:42.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,My name is Momoko Ozono.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.86,0:34:47.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm from Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.86,0:34:53.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please call me Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.86,0:34:55.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,Momoko. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.86,0:34:59.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,You haven't asked her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.86,0:35:07.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,What do you do on a holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.86,0:35:13.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,I go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.29,0:35:16.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.29,0:35:17.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.29,0:35:21.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan, please give her a reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.29,0:35:23.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,You asked her a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.29,0:35:26.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore her when she answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.29,0:35:27.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.29,0:35:29.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Reaction is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.29,0:35:31.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,You go shopping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:32.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.29,0:35:34.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.29,0:35:35.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.29,0:35:36.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's right. I go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.29,0:35:38.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,You should have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.29,0:35:39.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,I go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.29,0:35:43.29,ASS,,0,0,0,,"Go shopping" is "I go shopping".
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.06,0:35:48.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,"To" doesn't go in before "shopping", so\Nbe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.06,0:35:53.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,My name is Minami Umezawa. I'm from...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.06,0:36:00.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please look at the person who is\Ntalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.06,0:36:06.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm from Kanagawa. Please call me\NMinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:08.06,ASS,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.78,0:36:15.78,ASS,,0,0,0,,What is your least favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:22.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Can you take a picture of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.09,0:36:28.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.09,0:36:31.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Or least favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.09,0:36:33.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Don't answer questions with questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.09,0:36:35.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.09,0:36:38.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.09,0:36:39.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.09,0:36:42.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.53,0:36:44.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I'm Suica"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.53,0:36:45.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,The teacher has changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.53,0:36:47.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:48.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's "I'm Suica".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.53,0:36:51.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,What does "I'm Suica" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.53,0:36:53.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,It means "I'm Suica".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.53,0:36:57.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to say "Suica" in\NEnglish?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.53,0:36:58.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:36:59.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.53,0:37:00.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.53,0:37:02.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Christy, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.53,0:37:03.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,Watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.53,0:37:06.53,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I don't like watermelon."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.53,0:37:09.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,"I don't like watermelon."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.26,0:37:12.26,ASS,,0,0,0,,My least favorite food is watermelon.
